I was raised as a conservative small town country girl and moved to the city and got a taste of reality. I ran away from home (without telling anyone) after I found out a dark family secret. I had no idea what was going to happen next.
 Coming to the city, I was able to experience a lot of firsts and get in touch with the side of me that was sheltered away. My experiences are what inspires my music. I've been singing all of my life, and sang in choir in church. I was never able to listen to music on the radio, but now that side of me is history. I think everyone should be in touch with their deeper, darker and sexy side... Which is what I live by now!

Ava Thompson is a multi-talented singer, songwriter, producer, and sound engineer hailing from England. She is signed to Mandem Records in Los Santos and is making a name for herself in the pop and R&B music scene. Her music is characterized by catchy melodies, powerful vocals, and relatable lyrics that speak to the experiences of her listeners.
 Ava's passion for music started at an early age, and she has been honing her craft ever since. She is a versatile artist who can play several instruments, including the piano and guitar. Her expertise in sound engineering and music production has given her a unique advantage in creating music that captivates her fans.
 With her talent, drive, and dedication, Ava Thompson is poised to become one of the biggest names in pop and R&B music. Her music continues to gain momentum, and fans around the world are eagerly anticipating what's next for this rising star.

Klaas2, a rising star in the world of alternative R&B, has been making waves with his unique blend of soulful melodies and introspective rap lyrics. Born and raised in Poland, this multifaceted artist's journey to Los Santos was anything but ordinary. Enduring a tumultuous divorce that left him with nothing, Klaas2 found solace and inspiration in music, using it as a means to heal and rise above life's challenges.
 As Klaas2 continues to evolve as an artist, we eagerly anticipate what the future holds for him. His undeniable talent and unwavering passion for music are the driving forces that will undoubtedly propel him to new heights in the industry. We are proud to support Klaas2 on his journey and look forward to sharing his music with the world.

Raiden Rufio is an Australian-born Filipino, musician and songwriter who is currently based in Los Santos. His influences include the Gorillaz, Arctic Monkeys and The Strokes. Rufio's music is a blend of rock and pop and his lyrics often explore themes of love, loss, and self-discovery.
 Rufio released his debut single, 'Hellhounds of the Sea' in 2022. The single was well-received by critics and fans alike, and it helped to establish Rufio as a rising star in the music industry. Rufio is a passionate and dedicated musician, and he is always looking for new ways to express himself through music.

Sydney, a brave artist, uses her music as a powerful tool for self-expression and empowerment. Drawing from her own experiences with DID and PTSD, she fearlessly addresses mental health and encourages others to embrace their uniqueness.
 Through soulful indie rock melodies and poignant lyrics, she creates a safe space for vulnerability, urging listeners to break free from societal expectations and speak their truth. Sydney's music serves as a beacon of hope, reminding us that embracing our differences is what truly makes us extraordinary.
